<i>And when I asked her again...</i>

24:03.500 --> 24:05.435
<i>she got very mad at me.</i>

24:10.039 --> 24:13.176
<i>I don't know
why she was so unhappy.</i>

24:16.111 --> 24:18.782
<i>Maybe it was just me.</i>

24:22.051 --> 24:25.120
<i>She wasn't always like that.</i>

24:45.108 --> 24:47.540
Baby...

24:47.542 --> 24:49.846
I'm sorry. I'm tired.

26:19.401 --> 26:21.300
Ah!

26:21.302 --> 26:22.603
