'cause I brought the gun.

31:30.745 --> 31:32.178
<i>Oh.</i>

31:32.180 --> 31:34.047
<i>That's not good.</i>

31:34.049 --> 31:35.415
<i>You got a big problem then.</i>

31:35.417 --> 31:37.149
