'cause I had to lie to her

32:00.342 --> 32:02.341
that this phone has no signal.

32:02.343 --> 32:05.879
<i>Oh. Why would you say that?</i>

32:05.881 --> 32:07.848
It's my only excuse
to get away,

32:07.850 --> 32:09.449
to try and get a signal
to make a call.

32:09.451 --> 32:11.684
