why you took her there.

32:58.434 --> 33:00.770
<i>The gallery
wasn't doing too good.</i>

33:03.606 --> 33:05.741
<i>I was gonna close it down.</i>

33:14.916 --> 33:19.222
<i>But then I got
this phone call...</i>

33:21.255 --> 33:25.427
<i>about this old native plaque.</i>

33:30.064 --> 33:32.031
<i>We're calling
to inform you, sir,</i>

33:32.033 --> 33:34.634
<i>that we have not received
rental payment for your gallery</i>

33:34.636 --> 33:36.502
<i>for over 60 days.</i>

33:36.504 --> 33:38.171
<i>Your current
outstanding balance</i>

33:38.173 --> 33:40.876
<i>must be paid
within five business days.</i>

33:42.878 --> 33:45.244
<i>Sir?</i>

33:45.246 --> 33:47.550
