if you like them.

34:11.940 --> 34:13.206
Yes. They're beautiful.

34:21.583 --> 34:23.849
He's saying that this collection
brings him good luck,

34:23.851 --> 34:26.453
but to their people,
it can be quite the opposite,

34:26.455 --> 34:28.487
and he wants to know
if you know why.

34:28.489 --> 34:30.255
I'm not exactly sure.

34:34.397 --> 34:36.565
