with its history.

35:46.634 --> 35:50.136
<i>I found out
that it was placed there</i>

35:50.138 --> 35:55.610
<i>to commemorate
a small tragic event.</i>

35:56.878 --> 35:58.744
<i>That's why the locals
are afraid</i>

35:58.746 --> 36:00.616
<i>to set foot on that island.</i>

36:03.518 --> 36:06.489
<i>They believe that there's
something protecting it.</i>

36:13.696 --> 36:15.063
<i>I felt it.</i>

36:16.197 --> 36:18.500
<i>But somehow...</i>

36:19.835 --> 36:22.705
<i>it seemed to draw her in.</i>

36:53.067 --> 36:56.171
<i>She seemed to be
so curious about it.</i>

36:59.406 --> 37:01.643
<i>Like a siren.</i>

37:22.964 --> 37:26.333
<i>I wasn't afraid
of the creature.</i>

37:26.335 --> 37:28.838
<i>They were just tales.</i>

37:30.438 --> 37:33.542
<i>She seemed to be
in a different world.</i>

37:35.743 --> 37:38.213
<i>But it was scaring me.</i>

37:41.882 --> 37:44.819
<i>It was beyond her grief.</i>

37:46.522 --> 37:48.523
<i>It was something...</i>

37:49.857 --> 37:51.759
