43:07.542 --> 43:08.844
No.

43:10.179 --> 43:12.679
I don't know.
I don't remember.

43:12.681 --> 43:14.416
Hey.

43:15.851 --> 43:17.817
Are you okay?

43:17.819 --> 43:18.954
Yeah.

43:21.623 --> 43:23.021
Yeah, you are.

43:23.023 --> 43:25.625
Let's just change
the bandage tomorrow.

43:25.627 --> 43:27.228
I'm sure it'll be fine.

